      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The exterior has significant cosmetic damage, including deep scratches, several large dents, and noticeable rust bubbling on the door panels and wheel wells. Mechanically, the engine runs but requires immediate professional attention due to a rough idle and fluid leaks, and the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. It is being sold strictly as-is.",
