    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a mechanically sorted example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L atmospheric inline-six features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, providing an urgent, linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Shifting is handled by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power distribution. The chassis is in strong driver condition, featuring reinforced rear subframe mounting points and refreshed bushings to maintain structural rigidity under lateral load. With documented valve clearances and a consistent compression profile, this M3 offers a visceral, analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
